@page "/privacy-policy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy — Katie's Garden</PageTitle>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <div role="alert" class="alert alert-warning mb-8">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
        </svg>
        <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">REQUIRES REVIEW</p>
            <p class="text-sm">This policy is a placeholder and must be reviewed and approved by Katie or a qualified legal adviser before the site goes live.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold text-base-content mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-base-content/50 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: @DateTime.UtcNow.ToString("MMMM yyyy")</p>

    <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none">

        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>Katie's Garden is a garden services and plant sales business based in Milverton, Somerset, TA4. When you use our website or place an order, we collect and process your personal data as described in this policy.</p>
        <p>You can contact us at: <a href="mailto:team@katiesgarden.uk">team@katiesgarden.uk</a></p>

        <h2>What data we collect and why</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Name, email address, and phone number</strong> — collected when you place an order or contact us, so we can fulfil your order and communicate with you about it.</li>
            <li><strong>Delivery address</strong> — collected only if you choose local delivery, so we can deliver your order.</li>
            <li><strong>Order details</strong> — items purchased, quantities, and prices, for order fulfilment and our records.</li>
            <li><strong>Newsletter subscription</strong> — your email address if you choose to subscribe, so we can send you occasional updates.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Payments</h2>
        <p>All payments are processed by <strong>Stripe</strong>. We never see or store your card details. Stripe's privacy policy is available at <a href="https://stripe.com/gb/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">stripe.com/gb/privacy</a>.</p>

        <h2>How we store your data</h2>
        <p>Order and contact data is stored securely in our database hosted in Microsoft Azure (UK region). We retain order records for 7 years to meet UK tax obligations. Contact and newsletter data is retained until you ask us to remove it.</p>

        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>Under UK GDPR you have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:team@katiesgarden.uk">team@katiesgarden.uk</a>.</p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use a single browser-based storage item (localStorage) to remember the contents of your shopping basket. This is not a tracking cookie and is stored only on your device.</p>

        <h2>Third parties</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services: Stripe (payments), Microsoft Azure (hosting and database), and Brevo (newsletter). We do not sell your data to any third party.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this policy, please email <a href="mailto:team@katiesgarden.uk">team@katiesgarden.uk</a>.</p>
    </div>
</div>
